snippet.title: STARIMU - Tour & Game Showcase!!
snippet.description:
I recently got into play Starimu and I wanted to show it off in hopes of other players joining! 
.
Starimu is a virtual world inspired by others such as Fantage and Club Penguin where you can dress up your character, play minigames, and chat with like-minded people from all over the world. It's free to play, you just have to download it and get started!
.
.
.
.
Starimu Website: https://starimu.com
instagram: https://www.instagram.com/far0n.starimu
tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@far0n.starimu
.
